Ali is a common non-player character name in Gielinor, especially in the Kharidian Desert.

  • Prince Ali, the prince of Al-Kharid
  • Drunken Ali, a drunk man drinking
  • Ali Morrisane, the dealer involved in the Rogue Trader minigame
  • Ali the Barman, owns The Asp & Snake Bar
  • Ali the Camel, a talking camel
  • Ali the Camel Man
  • Ali the Carter, water salesman
  • Ali the dyer, a woman in Pollnivneach
  • Ali the Farmer, in Al Kharid
  • Ali the Guard, in Al Kharid
  • Ali the Hag, a witch
  • Ali the Kebab seller, kebab shop owner
  • Ali the Leaflet Dropper
  • Ali the Mayor, mayor of Pollnivneach
  • Ali the Operator, leader of the Menaphite Thugs
  • Ali the Sandsweeper
  • Ali the Smith, a blacksmith
  • Ali the Snake Charmer, a snake charmer
  • Ali the Tailor
  • Traitorous Ali, a member of the Menaphites
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
